B.a_D=new A.aR(B.dX,["1. Platform Overview","Skill Passport India is a private EdTech platform facilitating access to NSQF-aligned skill courses (NIELIT, NSDC/SSC, CBSE), tracking community service credits, and connecting students to college admission pathways under NEP 2020/NCrF."],t.li)
B.a_C=new A.aR(B.dX,["2. Revenue Model","Skill Passport earns 10% of all training transactions. Trainers earn 90%. Exam fees go to NIELIT/NSDC directly \u2014 Skill Passport charges \u20b950 booking service fee. School plans are annual platform subscriptions."],t.li)
B.a_A=new A.aR(B.dX,["3. Community Service Credits","Community service credits on Skill Passport are verified by trainers/admins but are indicative. Final credit acceptance for college admission is subject to the respective university/institution's policy. Skill Passport cannot guarantee credit acceptance \u2014 we help you document and present your service record accurately."],t.li)
B.a_F=new A.aR(B.dX,["4. Certificate Disclaimer","Skill Passport issues Platform Achievement Certificates as internal records. Government certificates (NIELIT, NSDC, CBSE) are issued by the respective government bodies on passing their exams. Our certificates complement but do not replace government-issued credentials."],t.li)
B.a_H=new A.aR(B.dX,["5. Data & Privacy","Aadhaar is AES-256 encrypted; only last 4 digits stored. APAAR ID used with consent for ABC credit fetch. Community service data stored and shared only with the verifying trainer and student."],t.li)
B.a_B=new A.aR(B.dX,["6. Governing Law","Courts of Ahmedabad, Gujarat have exclusive jurisdiction. Platform governed by IT Act 2000, DPDP Act 2023, and Consumer Protection Act 2019."],t.li)
